summary: I am the kind of person, that never says no to  challenge, and will continue on it until it has either been smashed or taught me something valuable from it. A quote that summarizes how I operate, from the movie Rocky, "You, me, or nobody is gonna hit as hard as life. But it ain't about how hard you hit. It's about how hard you can get hit and keep moving forward; how much you can take and keep moving forward. That's how winning is done!"
